name: Mi Reino: New Silver/White
description: Mi Cuerpo, Mi Reino My Body, My Kingdom Love Out Loud isn't only about loving others, its about loving yourself and living life to the fullest. Your body is your kingdom, your domain. Reign strong and live well. The heraldic lion is a symbol of strength and wisdom. Wear it proud and Love Out Loud! Inspired by and dedicated in loving memory to the one and only Alicia Jovita Quintana, a large portion of the proceeds will go directly to the Alicia Jovita Quintana Memorial Scholarship... Special shout out to Kelly Egan-Thorpe for inspiring the concept! Much love, Kel. Printed on
